{
  "message": "test(masked): wire count/cumsum/cumprod/median/ptp conformance coverage\n\nAdded 9 differential goldens across 5 previously unwired MaskedArray\noperations:\n- count: flat count (expected_scalar=5), per-column (axis=0), per-row (axis=1)\n- cumsum: 1D with masked middle, mask preserved on output\n- cumprod: 1D with masked second element, mask preserved\n- median: odd unmasked count (\u21924), even unmasked count (\u21922.5)\n- ptp: ignores masked extremes (5,8,1,4 \u2192 7)\n\nRegistered the five operations in execute_masked_differential_operation.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
